# EAS Build archive 阶段忽略规则
# 位置：仓库根（ProClaw/），因为 EAS CLI 19.1.0 在 git 仓库根（rev-parse --show-toplevel）找 .easignore
# 如果仓库根没有 .easignore，EAS 会退回到 fast-glob('**/.gitignore') 读取所有子目录的 .gitignore
# 而仓库根 .gitignore 含 `*.png` 会误排除 mobile/assets/*.png 导致 PREBUILD ENOENT
# 详见：mobile/.tmp-eas-src/package/build/vcs/local.js:48-78

# === Node 依赖 ===
node_modules/
**/node_modules/

# === Qoder IDE 缓存（中文路径会让 EAS archive 中止）===
.qoder/
**/.qoder/
../.qoder/

# === 本地调试日志与解压中间产物 ===
dist-*/
**/dist-*/
dist-eas-log*.txt
dist-eas-log*.gz

# === 临时文件 ===
*.log
**/*.log
*.tmp
**/*.tmp
.cache/
**/.cache/
.tmp*
**/.tmp*
**/dist-eas-*

# === Expo / Web build ===
.expo/
**/.expo/
dist/
**/dist/
web-build/

# === IDE & Editor ===
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
.codebuddy/
**/.codebuddy/

# === OS ===
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# === Environment ===
.env.local
.env.*.local
**/.env*.local

# === Database ===
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal

# === Test / Coverage ===
playwright-report/
test-results/
.blob-report/
playwright/.cache/
coverage/
.nyc_output/
vitest.config.ts.timestamp-*

# === Native build artifacts ===
.kotlin/
*.orig.*
*.jks
*.p8
*.p12
*.key
*.mobileprovision

# === macOS / Security ===
*.pem

# === TypeScript ===
*.tsbuildinfo
expo-env.d.ts

# === Metro ===
.metro-health-check*

# === Generated native folders (must be re-generated by EAS prebuild) ===
mobile/android/
mobile/ios/
/ios
/android
**/android/
**/ios/

# === Tauri ===
src-tauri/target/

# === Marketing site ===
marketing-site/dist/

# === Mobile build outputs ===
mobile/dist-web*/

# === Docs（太大）===
docs/
audit/
audits/
coverage-reports/

# === 临时调试脚本（避免误传到 EAS）===
mobile/scripts/fix-*.js
mobile/scripts/patch-*.js
mobile/scripts/replace-*.js
**/scripts/fix-*.js
**/scripts/patch-*.js

# === 测试截图（仓库根 .gitignore 里有 *.png 规则，必须在 .easignore 中保留但反向包含 assets/）===
*.png
**/*.png

# === 反向规则：必须保留 mobile/assets/ 下的 PNG 文件 ===
# 这是修复 PREBUILD ENOENT 的关键
# app.json 引用了以下 PNG：
#   - ./assets/proclaw-logo.png
#   - ./assets/android-icon-foreground.png
#   - ./assets/android-icon-background.png
#   - ./assets/android-icon-monochrome.png
#   - ./assets/splash-icon.png
!mobile/assets/
!mobile/assets/**
!mobile/assets/*.png
!mobile/assets/**/*.png